headline: Chipotle (CMG): Assessing Valuation After Q3 Revenue Miss and Management’s No-Discount Strategy
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (CMG) shares have faced renewed pressure after the company reported a third-quarter revenue miss alongside a drop in foot traffic. In response, management made it clear they will not cut prices or offer discounts. Instead, they are focusing on protecting the brand’s long-term value.
